Storgue</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=2d2e3f><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub30.ezboard.com/uazraelmoonwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Azrael Moonwolf</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>280</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#6F6F6F>4/5/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#6F6F6F>6:39:36 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://cryofthewolf.tripod.com/azrael7.jpg width = 121 hieght = 315></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: 4-4 patch </font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Get the skins and patterns and I'll make any you need for free all night long, provided they are for your use.<br>
<br>
Verant did say that these packs now have 10% weight reduction, and if you right-click and hold on any container now it will tell you what it's weight reduction is, if any. <br>
<br>
Handmade backpacks now weight the same as every other buyable combinable container, but have weight reduction and 2 more slots, so I suspect I'll be making a lot of these for many people.<br>
<br>
